<view class="page data-v-efa45563"><view class="header data-v-efa45563"><text class="header-title data-v-efa45563">AI运营评估</text><text class="header-sub data-v-efa45563">龟钮印证实时加权值引擎</text></view><view a:if="{{a}}" class="loading data-v-efa45563"><text class="data-v-efa45563">分析中...</text></view><view a:else class="data-v-efa45563"><view class="quick-stats data-v-efa45563"><view class="qs-item data-v-efa45563"><text class="qs-val gold data-v-efa45563">¥{{b}}</text><text class="qs-lbl data-v-efa45563">累计收益</text></view><view class="qs-item data-v-efa45563"><text class="qs-val data-v-efa45563">{{c}}</text><text class="qs-lbl data-v-efa45563">内容数</text></view><view class="qs-item data-v-efa45563"><text class="qs-val accent data-v-efa45563">{{d}}</text><text class="qs-lbl data-v-efa45563">KOL评分</text></view></view><view class="score-ring data-v-efa45563"><text class="score-val data-v-efa45563" style="{{'color:' + f}}">{{e}}</text><text class="score-lbl data-v-efa45563">综合评分</text></view><view class="insight-list data-v-efa45563"><view a:for="{{g}}" a:for-item="item" a:key="i" class="insight-card data-v-efa45563"><view class="insight-left data-v-efa45563"><view class="insight-icon data-v-efa45563" style="{{'background:' + item.b}}"><text class="icon-text data-v-efa45563">{{item.a}}</text></view></view><view class="insight-right data-v-efa45563"><view class="insight-top data-v-efa45563"><text class="insight-title data-v-efa45563">{{item.c}}</text><text class="insight-score data-v-efa45563" style="{{'color:' + item.e}}">{{item.d}}分</text></view><text class="insight-desc data-v-efa45563">{{item.f}}</text><progress class="data-v-efa45563" percent="{{item.g}}" stroke-width="4" activeColor="{{item.h}}" backgroundColor="#e5e7eb"/></view></view></view><view class="tips-section data-v-efa45563"><text class="tips-title data-v-efa45563">AI运营建议</text><view class="tip-card data-v-efa45563"><text class="tip-text data-v-efa45563">1. 保持每日至少1条原创内容发布，提升内容质量分</text></view><view class="tip-card data-v-efa45563"><text class="tip-text data-v-efa45563">2. 增加与粉丝互动频次，提升传播力加权值</text></view><view class="tip-card data-v-efa45563"><text class="tip-text data-v-efa45563">3. 选择与个人品牌契合的KOL任务，转化率更高</text></view><view class="tip-card data-v-efa45563"><text class="tip-text data-v-efa45563">4. 龟钮印证存证内容可提升0.15x乘数奖励</text></view></view></view></view>